description: Stunning 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo on the 36th floor of the prestigious CIRRUS tower featuring floor-to-ceiling windows with captivating city skyline views. This 687 square foot home showcases wide-plank hardwood floors, custom Snaidero cabinetry, Dornbracht fixtures, and quartz countertops with beautiful tile backsplash throughout. The kitchen is equipped with high-end Gaggenau and Bosch appliances and soaring 9-foot ceilings enhance the open feel. In unit washer dryer installed in 2023.  CIRRUS offers over 48,000 square feet of resort-style amenities including state-of-the-art fitness center, indoor lap pool, 24-hour concierge service, and landscaped rooftop terraces. The 41st-floor chef's kitchen provides stunning Lake Michigan views along with outdoor pool areas, fire pits, and grilling stations. Additional amenities include work spaces, entertainment areas, pet facilities with dog run, and bike storage.  Prime Lakeshore East location provides walkable access to Millennium Park, Lakefront Trail, and downtown dining and entertainment. This move-in ready residence INCLUDES garage parking and is available fully furnished. Contact listing agent for furnished package details. Experience luxury living in one of Chicago's most desirable waterfront neighborhoods.
